er]] (1332) & [[Christine Wolf (golfer)|Christine Wolf]]\n|}\n\n==Results==\n===Men's team===\n\n{{Main|2018 European Golf Team Championships - Men's team}}\n\n====Pool play====\nTeams were divided into 4 groups of 4 teams and played round-robin matches Wednesday to Friday using the fourball format.\n*Round 1 \u2013 8 August\n*Round 2 \u2013 9 August\n*Round 3 \u2013 10 August\n\n{| style=\"width: 60em\"\n|valign=top| \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Group A\n! Round !! Winner !! Score !! Loser\n|-\n| align=center rowspan=2|1 || Great Britain 1 || align=center|halved || Spain 2\n|-\n| '''Sweden 2''' || align=center|1 up || Sweden 1\n|-\n| align=center rowspan=2|2 || '''Great Britain 1''' || align=center|6 & 5 || Sweden 1\n|-\n| '''Spain 2''' || align=center|1  up || Sweden 2\n|-\n| align=center rowspan=2|3 || '''Sweden 2''' || align=center|3 & 2 || Great Britain 1\n|-\n| '''Spain 2''' || align=center|3 & 2 || Sweden 1\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! Seed !! Player !! W !! L !! H !! Points !! Finish\n|-\n| 8 || align=left|{{ESP}} 2 || 2 || 0 || 1 || 5 || 1\n|-\n| 16 || align=left|{{SWE}} 2 || 2 || 1 || 0 || 4 || 2\n|-\n| 1 || align=left|{{GBR2}} 1 || 1 || 1 || 1 || 3 || 3\n|-\n| 9 || align=left|{{SWE}} 1 || 0 || 3 || 0 || 0 || 4\n|}\n \n|valign=top| \n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+ Group B\n! Round !! Winner !! Score !! Loser\n|-\n| align=center rowspan=2|1 || '''Great Britain 3''' || align=center|4 & 3 || Great Britain 2\n|-\n| '''Italy 2''' || align=center|2 & 1 || Ireland\n|-\n| align=center rowspan=2|2 || '''Italy 2''' || align=center|2 & 1 || Great Britain 2\n|-\n| '''Great Britain 3''' || align=center|2 & 1 || Ireland\n|-\n| align=center rowspan=2|3 || '''Ireland''' || align=center|4 & 3 || Great Britain 2\n|-\n| '''Italy 2''' || align=center|1 up || Great Britain 3\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! Seed !! Player !! W !! L !! H !! Points !! Finish\n|-\n| 12 || align=left|{{ITA}} 2 || 3 || 0 || 0 || 6 || 1\n|-\n| 5 ||