 of countries|Country]]\n|subdivision_name = {{flag|Iran}}\n|subdivision_type1 =[[Provinces of Iran|Province]]\n|subdivision_name1 =[[Sistan and Baluchestan Province|Sistan and Baluchestan]]\n|subdivision_type2 =[[Counties of Iran|County]]\n|subdivision_name2 = [[Mehrestan County|Mehrestan]]\n|subdivision_type3 =[[Bakhsh]]\n|subdivision_name3 =[[Ashar District|Ashar]]\n|subdivision_type4 =[[Rural Districts of Iran|Rural District]]\n|subdivision_name4 =[[Irafshan Rural District|Irafshan]]\n|leader_title           = \n|leader_name            = \n|established_title      =\n|established_date       = \n|area_total_km2           = \n|area_footnotes           = \n|population_as_of         = 2006\n|population_total =24\n|population_density_km2   =auto\n|timezone               = [[Iran Standard Time|IRST]]\n|utc_offset             = +3:30\n|timezone_DST           = [[Iran Daylight Time|IRDT]]\n|utc_offset_DST         = +4:30\n|coordinates            = \n|elevation_m            = \n|area_code              = \n|website                = \n|footnotes              =\n}}\n'''Hansan''' ({{lang-fa|\u062d\u0646\u0633\u0627\u0646}}, also [[Romanize]]d as '''\u1e28ans\u0101n''') is a village in [[Irafshan Rural District]], [[Ashar District]], [[Mehrestan County]], [[Sistan and Baluchestan Province]], [[Iran]]. At the 2006 census, its population was 24, in 5 families.<ref>{{IranCensus2006|11}}</ref>\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Mehrestan County}}\n\n{{coord missing|Sistan and Baluchestan Province}}\n\n{{Portal|Iran}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Mehrestan County]]\n\n\n{{Mehrestan-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Dean197", "label": "safe", "comment": "Minor copy change", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hansan,_Iran"}
